1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with dense object modeling from RGBD images, which is a core topic in computer vision. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as simultaneous localization and mapping (SLAM) is a common problem in robotics. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper mentions the use of deep end-to-end models for solving geometric localization and mapping problems. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is possible as the paper deals with the use of shape priors, which is a common topic in AI. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is possible as the paper deals with 3D object reconstruction, which is a common topic in computer graphics.
